# Public-repo policy for this project:
#
#   Only .c, .syscfg, .projectspec, README.md and .gitignore are
#   committed to GitHub.  Everything else (build artefacts, CCS
#   workspace metadata, generated SysConfig output, copied SDK source
#   files, board PDFs, etc.) stays local.
#
# This file is allowlist-style: deny everything first, then re-allow
# the specific filename patterns the policy permits.  Files matching
# the explicit deny rules at the bottom remain ignored even if the
# allow rules would otherwise let them through (the deny rules are
# there to cover generated artefacts that share an allowed extension,
# e.g. a SysConfig-generated *.c that lands inside a project folder).

# 1. Deny everything by default.
*

# 2. Re-allow directory recursion so git can walk subprojects.
!*/

# 3. Re-allow the file types listed in the policy.
!.gitignore
!README.md
!LICENSE
!*.c
!*.syscfg
!*.projectspec

# 3b. Per-project header allow rule for foc_eth_drive. The project is
#     hand-coded against driverlib without SysConfig, so its public
#     surface lives in several .h files that the .c files depend on.
#     Other projects keep the original header-free policy.
!foc_eth_drive/**/*.h

# 4. Explicitly re-deny generated outputs and SDK copies that may
#    sit next to source files after a build or first import.
syscfg/
Debug/
Release/
CPU1_RAM/
CPU1_FLASH/
CM_RAM/
CM_FLASH/
targetConfigs/
device/
.settings/
.metadata/
.theia/
.vscode/
.idea/

# 5. Local-only files that are NOT considered project source.
true
HW_Documentations/
_archived_previous_attempts/
# CCS workspace auto-renames a project when it can't reuse the same
# name on re-import; any duplicate folder is not source, do not commit.
*_2/
cm_ethernet_2/

# 6. C2000Ware SDK source files that the projectspec copies into a
#    project on import.  These are TI's code, not ours - they belong
#    in C2000Ware, not in this repo.
adc_ethernet_scope/adc_scope_cm/device_cm.c
adc_ethernet_scope/adc_scope_cm/enet.c
adc_ethernet_scope/adc_scope_cm/f2838xif.c
adc_ethernet_scope/adc_scope_cm/lwiplib.c
adc_ethernet_scope/adc_scope_cm/pinout.c
adc_ethernet_scope/adc_scope_cm/startup_ccs.c
foc_eth_drive/foc_eth_drive_cm/device_cm.c
foc_eth_drive/foc_eth_drive_cm/enet.c
foc_eth_drive/foc_eth_drive_cm/f2838xif.c
foc_eth_drive/foc_eth_drive_cm/lwiplib.c
foc_eth_drive/foc_eth_drive_cm/pinout.c
foc_eth_drive/foc_eth_drive_cm/startup_ccs.c
foc_eth_drive/foc_eth_drive_cm/lwipopts.h
foc_eth_drive/foc_eth_drive_cm/lwippools.h
